markets.title: Will Kamala Harris become the next Justice on the Supreme Court?
markets.subtitle: Kamala Harris
markets.rules_primary: If Kamala Harris is the first person confirmed by the U.S. Senate to the position of Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States in the period between Issuance and January 20, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
Likewise, the market resolves to No if no person is confirmed by January 20, 2025.

The market will expire at the sooner of the first 10:00 AM following the confirmation of any individual to the position of Justice of the Supreme Court, Congress.gov updating for January 20, 2025, or February 03, 2025. The market will close at the sooner of the first 10:00 AM following the confirmation of any individual to the position of Justice of the Supreme Court, or 11:59 PM ET on January 20, 2025.
